“Har-are-yuh? Is Har-are-yuh here?”

“Sea-mus? Do I got a Sea-mus in here?”
“It’s Seamus.”
“Yo name’s Sea-mus!”

“Her-my-one? Is there Her-my-one? No Her-my-one? I swear to god, if y’all give me one of yo silly-ass names, this whole class is gonna feel my wrath.”
“Here.”
“Okay, Her-my-one. Why didn’t you answer the first time?”
“What?”
“Because, you know, I called yo name like, five times.”
“Because it’s Hermione.”
“SON OF A-“ flips crap. “Ya done messed up, Her-my-one! Get yo ass to Dummlay-dooray’s office!”
“Dumbledore?”
“GET OUT!”
“Okay.”

“Okay, Rone?”
“Present.
“THANK you.”
